text: Jatropha unicostata is a species of plant in the family Euphorbiaceae. It is endemic to Socotra island Yemen. Its name in Soqotri is "sibru". Its natural habitat is subtropical or tropical dry forests. ==References== Category:Endemic flora of Socotra unicostata Category:Least concern plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot Category:Plants described in 1884 Category:Taxa named by Isaac Bayley Balfour
